room_title: Escape room "Shawshank v2" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Wilmington in Wilmington (DE)
room_description: Derived from our most popular room in Newark, we bring you a second and more immersive version! You will literally have to escape prison in order to accomplish this experience. Based on a prison theme, you will need to work together in order to get each other out of your cells.
